{"tid":1272133,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實民陣算係咁","createTime":"2019-07-01T09:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T10:03:44.000Z","uid":222302,"like":87,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"eab4df28a082945803a4315cc58a113047c0a2af","tid":1272133,"uid":222302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:11:42.000Z","msg":"民陣、議員係制度內嘅戰士<br />\n我哋係制度外嘅戰士<br />\n唔可以有完全100%一模一樣嘅expectation<br />\n<br />\n如果民陣都叫衝呀衝呀<br />\n大家想下次邊個吹雞同申請不反對通知書呢？<br />\n淨係想叫下口號嘅師奶仔又可以信任邊個嘅平台支持學生呢？<br />\n佢算係咁啦 去到遮打道 大家識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n議員大部分嘅票都來自和理非<br />\n唔係話佢哋點阻都啱晒<br />\n只係想呼籲 體諒吓<br />\n佢哋要為我哋在制度內發聲啊<br />\n<br />\n最後 不割蓆 打死不割<br />\n多謝義士 多謝你嘅一份勇氣<br />\n係香港無法好好守護你哋 先官逼民反<br />\n<br />\n衝咗都係為我哋爭取咋<br />\n再講 都發生咗 值得我哋好好支持好好守護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最重要係團結 槍外對外<br />\n屌林鄭老母 屌黑警老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4795cf25c7dcb796687f67bb018758a7f658dcfa","tid":1272133,"uid":222302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:13:31.000Z","msg":"偷偷推自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c786951595247879ca39cac2020f20ea9ceece84","tid":1272133,"uid":222302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:13:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"232049862aa8b5e43da96efc8b18c1fc616b8654","tid":1272133,"uid":105578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:14:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca3bdd13b184a4948187d0e3fc32e0adda7c4cd9","tid":1272133,"uid":222302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:14:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d61c065a61a84c6405bdee90c61b4b08de09567","tid":1272133,"uid":222302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:15:36.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"670849a6609df53f23fc047a0bd002acbaac64cf","tid":1272133,"uid":835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:16:38.000Z","msg":"總之和理非同勇武同一陣線"},{"pid":"ec41fad0535533f32a3799e24a2ef699a0465bc1","tid":1272133,"uid":183890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:17:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好再問有無鬼<br />\n<br />\n與其被分化，不如相信前線一樣有判斷能力，或者加入現場決策，我哋需要團結，而唔係互相指責。<br />\n<br />\n假如真係有鬼，我哋更加要到現場保護前線手足，而唔係坐喺度望住佢哋犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n如果20國嘅香港人可以團結，我哋都可以。<br />\n<br />\n如果你曾經認同過「無論雞蛋多麼錯誤，我永遠站在雞蛋一方」這句說話，希望各位毋忘初心。 <br />\n<br />\n齊上齊落，不撤不散。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"be4010809f9a4b6026f221b66bbcb8633bf3a66c","tid":1272133,"uid":3273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:17:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5ca3321e8a373fc1b312fc2f9dff0af468c7199","tid":1272133,"uid":263221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:18:13.000Z","msg":"推，講得幾岩"},{"pid":"a0037fadf977120a43096b6376a88992aeb035fa","tid":1272133,"uid":104980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:20:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cec55b3690faf4779ef456da6774efc7034b3932","tid":1272133,"uid":222302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:20:29.000Z","msg":"推吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f513d8a82a9691e498eccab8fde3a206c8283bb6","tid":1272133,"uid":183890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:20:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84b9b895eb84723ed7d89b3dce32c3a39b86779d","tid":1272133,"uid":91616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,